  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. The model was revised in early 2026 to incorporate updated impeller geometry tolerances and revised turbulence model constants; however, the primary experimental validation dataset retains a dataVintage from the prior quarter and has not yet been superseded. Re-validation against a post-revision dataset is planned but not yet executed.",
