    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/cou2-vad-decision-2026q1",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-assessment-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the model for the VAD COU subject to conditions. All 13 credibility factors were assessed; achieved levels fall below required levels in all cases, consistent with the Low assurance classification. The primary validation dataset (FDA pump PIV and hemolysis bench data, vintage 2025-Q4) and the blood rheology material properties dataset (vintage 2025-Q3) were collected prior to the January 2026 model revision. Re-validation of the updated model against a post-revision experimental dataset is planned for Q2 2026. The team judged the residual gap acceptable given the conservative hemolysis threshold margin observed in output comparisons, and accepted the submission pending completion of the planned re-validation activity.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
